These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, aconite, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Flower   | aconite | poppy | rose | balloon-flower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, apricot, spinach, strawberry
1. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | spinach | apricot | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, brazilian, nigerian, spanish
1. the nigerian is on the left of the french##1
2. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the brazilian is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality   | nigerian | french | brazilian | spanish |

