.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, skydiving, camping
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | camping | skydiving | woodworking | video-games |

