.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, indie, blues, rock
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
3. the fan of rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |  2   |  3  |  4  |
| Music-Genre   | rock | disco | indie | blues |

